      "content": "okay i hear you but i'm kinda nervous about the doctor thing because i have a super busy week at work and i dont want to deal with the hassle right now. i read online that drinking way more water helps flush out excess stuff in your system. if i just drink a lot more water and keep taking it like usual, won't that just fix the nausea and the shakes on its own? i feel like i can handle it till the weekend.",
